OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAnother day of long sunny
OL,6,Fspells, though rather breezy once
OL,7,Fagain by afternoon. The strongest
OL,8,Fwinds near windward coasts and across
OL,9,Fhills. Warm inland but cooler along
OL,10,Fthe coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA fine evening leading into a
OL,13,Fdry and chilly night with long clear
OL,14,Fspells. Brisk winds near coasts easing
OL,15,Fa little through the night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
