OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FFriday, starting chilly then
OL,6,Fmostly fine through the day and
OL,7,Fturning very warm by afternoon.
OL,8,FSunshine becoming increasingly hazy,
OL,9,Fwith cloud bringing a risk of showers
OL,10,Flater.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,13,FCloudier over the weekend and into
OL,14,FMonday with an increased chance of
OL,15,Frain or showers, probably heavy and
OL,16,Fthundery at times. Temperatures
OL,17,Freturning to near normal with
OL,18,Fgenerally light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
